Hopewell says not in talks with Everbright . Hopewell Holdings Ltd said in a statement on Friday that it was not in negotiations with the China Everbright group regarding a possible acquisition of a Hopewell stake by Everbright . The statement was made at the request of the Stock Exchange of Hong Kong following a rise of HK $ 0 . 60 in Hopewell shares to HK $ 5 . 30 on Thursday amid speculation that China Everbright Holdings Co Ltd could take a stake in the company . - - Hong Kong newsroom ( 852 ) 2843 6345 
